3rd Dia. Joseki
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fswiss\fcharset0 Tahoma;}{\f1\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1043\f0\fs18 Black has to play 1, White plays 2 and Black 3 is very important. If Black plays A instead of 3 the result is bad for Black.
\par White would answer B if Black played A.
\par We will study about this later.\lang1042\f1
\par
