4th Dia. Mistake
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fswiss\fcharset0 Tahoma;}{\f1\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1043\f0\fs18 Black 1 is a bad move. White will play 2 and force Black to crawl in the second line. Black still has to connect at A. So White will get sente.\lang1042\f1
